aves from 2 mint sprigs, fish sauce, lime juice, chilli powder and sugar in mixing bowl then chop <b>5 sec\/speed 6<b>. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula."},{"content":"Add reserved drained chicken and remaining mint leaves then mix <b>10 sec\/\/speed 2<b> ."},{"content":"Arrange on little gem lettuce leaves on a platter with sliced cucumber and bean sprouts then sprinkle with reserved ground sticky rice, to taste, for an authentic nutty flavour."}],"hintsAndTricks":["Serve with tamarind sauce or other oriental sauce of choice on the side."],"basicInfo":["easy","15m","30m","4 portions"]}